duck: Queensland Reds - The Queensland Reds represent Queensland in the sport of rugby union in the Southern Hemisphere Super Rugby competition.

The Queensland Rugby Union, or QRU, is the governing body for the sport of rugby union within the state of Queensland in Australia.
